# 📊 Sensor Data Analysis

The sensing framework utilizes threshold-based classification for environmental evaluation.

Gas concentration readings are categorized into:
- Safe
- Moderate
- Hazardous

This enables rapid identification of abnormal environmental conditions and supports emergency monitoring workflows.

